data.description: Located in 55+ "Core" area of Menifee, previously called Sun City....This home is the largest model built in 1977, known as Medallion homes for their proposed clean profile of modern living...being an entirely all-electric residence.  Uniquely situated in this upper desert community, Presley homes show pride of ownership and are coveted by seniors, here in Southern California.  The floorplans boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths with an extension of additional 225 sq ft that was added by the previous owners onto the supersized family room, giving the home a little more than 2000 sq ft.  The owners recenty had the entire exterior of the house painted, and all windows are new, dual paned and screened, brand new Air Conditiong and Forced air heating has been installed, as well as a complete rain gutter system, to protect the home during the winter.  Low maintenance rocked  front and rear yard will free up your time to enjoy life, rather than attending to landscaping.  The home boasts a Super thick Roof with plenty of years to go.  We do have a Solar System that must be assumed by new buyer.  Call agent for details, but the system keeps the electric bill manageable.   This is a "senior only" community.  Low taxes and low HOA with community amenities will include a ClubHouse, 2 pools, Spa, Tennis Courts, Gym and many more.
